{"tid":2267953,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"馬道立：司法獨立原則與政治無關","createTime":"2020-11-02T12:23:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-03T07:27:00.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":55,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"474455be6c90cb07241067dc71df32038fd8bd96","tid":2267953,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T12:23:53.000Z","msg":"終審法院首席法官馬道立表示，司法獨立原則與政治無關，基本法列明香港享有司法獨立。司法機構是特區政府的三大機關之一，基本法明確、毫不含糊訂明本港司法機關的角色與責任。<br />\n<br />\n馬道立在「香港法律周」開幕儀式致辭時表示，司法機關不受任何影響，包括政治，法庭並不關心政治，只會根據法律原則，公平公正地行使權利。他又強調在法律面前人人平等，任何人都不能凌駕法律。他表示，法治是香港的特色，亦必須要受到珍惜及保護，任何一個地區均不能承受破壞法治的後果。<br />\n<br />\n馬道立指，根據基本法，香港可以聘用其他行使普通法的司法管豁區的終審法院非常任法官及律師。他又表示，要彰顯公義必定要認識法律，提到法律應該要可預測、明確及清晰，法院的裁決亦要公開透明，讓外界得知裁決內容。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1557969-20201102.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1557969-20201102.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Vpe8FAkBT2vLq%2FWrgjLHxeL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=6909f1c2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1557969-20201102.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=675e48d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1557969-20201102.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"7a903b7f4a64b3f642456108c03546c958d5dc0c","tid":2267953,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T12:24:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64985030fcde37516da270b72036fd283d870507","tid":2267953,"uid":273703,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T12:25:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"65696a2e8505a3a76074de915adcaf40a608795a","tid":2267953,"uid":79117,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T12:25:24.000Z",