like":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T12:32:14.000Z","msg":"講係咁講"},{"pid":"2eaaf67bb11a6b4171854f241585113541a6e074","tid":2267953,"uid":201512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T12:34:16.000Z","msg":"就算聽日共產黨立條唔愛國就要死的法律，法官都會依法判案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df8139f1fb5dc9dc818adda0dc728e089650724d","tid":2267953,"uid":88743,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ffd3cdb128339be96eaf61eaaf1cd3585f73c60a","tid":2267953,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce4decf1e5c78f2fa57f931973635c727205d8d8","tid":2267953,"uid":88743,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"65696a2e8505a3a76074de915adcaf40a608795a","tid":2267953,"uid":79117,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T12:25:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T12:29:19.000Z","msg":"有司法獨立<br />\n但獨立得黎無三權分立<br />\n係咪好難明呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T12:29:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T12:35:32.000Z","msg":"咁樣會唔會明多少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><ins>中華人民共和國憲法</ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong> 第二條 中華人民共和國的<span class=\"red\">一切權力屬於人民</span>。</strong></ins><br />\n 人民行使國家權力的機關是全國人民代表大會和地方各級人民代表大會。<br />\n 人民依照法律規定，通過各種途徑和形式，管理國家事務，管理經濟和文化事業，管理社會事務。<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong> 第三條 中華人民共和國的國家機構實行<span class=\"red\">民主集中制</span>的原則。</strong></ins><br />\n<span class=\"red\">全國人民代表大會和地方各級人民代表大會都由民主選舉產生，對人民負責，受人民監督。</span><br />\n國家行政機關、監察機關、審判機關、檢察機關都由人民代表大會產生，對它負責，受它監督。<br />\n中央和地方的國家機構職權的劃分，遵循在中央的統一領導下，充分發揮地方的主動性、積極性的原則。"},{"pid":"8bf0cb7bc7872e8cab3d443be980c548bcf40509","tid":2267953,"uid":333163,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T12:39:11.000Z","msg":"快必以言入罪法庭唔俾保釋，邊條7頭仲有面講司法獨立無關政治呀？搵條7含下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d056b82aca24fa2034f9d5a5d474d31db43daca","tid":2267953,"uid":6237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T12:40:16.000Z","msg":"人地就係知道你地只會守原則<br />\n先比人玩到聲到唔敢出<br />\n法律係人訂, 死守法律而唔變通就會好似今日香港咁<br />\n我相信有一日國際法庭問點解你地會咁做既時候<br />\n同納粹德軍講既野都所差無幾"},{"pid":"c8d3ef21e2855c43a6a7226932169f1d30c1ff71","tid":2267953,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T12:43:07.000Z","msg":"司法獨立呢樣野本身咪政治<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52aafae2753a052af259cbad3baa6dad3728a6fb","tid":2267953,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T12:43:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"076cb54d9e896c73d42fcfb96f5b7fdad645de76","tid":2267953,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T12:56:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c643968f19eb533924ca3e6251699b30f04273ea","tid":2267953,"uid":365024,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"474455be6c90cb07241067dc71df32038fd8bd96","tid":2267953,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T12:23:53.000Z","msg":"終審法院首席法官馬道立表示，司法獨立原則與政治無關，基本法列明香港享有司法獨立。司法機構是特區政府的三大機關之一，基本法明確、毫不含糊訂明本港司法機關的角色與責任。<br />\n<br />\n馬道立在「香港法律周」開幕儀式致辭時表示，司法機關不受任何影響，包括政治，法庭並不關心政治，只會根據法律原則，公平公正地行使權利。他又強調在法律面前人人平等，任何人都不能凌駕法律。他表示，法治是香港的特色，亦必須要受到珍惜及保護，任何一個地區均不能承受破壞法治的後果。<br />\n<br />\n馬道立指，根據基本法，香港可以聘用其他行使普通法的司法管豁區的終審法院非常任法官及律師。他又表示，要彰顯公義必定要認識法律，提到法律應該要可預測、明確及清晰，法院的裁決亦要公開透明，讓外界得知裁決內容。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1557969-20201102.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1557969-20201102.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Vpe8FAkBT2vLq%2FWrgjLHxeL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=6909f1c2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1557969-20201102.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=675e48d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1557969-20201102.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T13:00:16.000Z","msg":"個speech好neutral，同之前一樣重申返重要原則"},{"pid":"4754a889557c1f0d11d6d1b2633b3b572abe8ecd","tid":2267953,"uid":34869,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T13:01:12.000Z","msg":"法治邪教最高大祭司"},{"pid":"ac4f54c848da5f575338ed5d743278146d67ee83","tid":2267953,"uid":365024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d056b82aca24fa2034f9d5a5d474d31db43daca","tid":2267953,"uid":6237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T12:40:16.000Z","msg":"人地就係知道你地只會守原則<br />\n先比人玩到聲到唔敢出<br />\n法律係人訂, 死守法律而唔變通就會好似今日香港咁<br />\n我相信有一日國際法庭問點解你地會咁做既時候<br />\n同納粹德軍講既野都所差無幾"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T13:11:20.000Z","msg":"你覺得佢「食古不化」定係變到好似十一哥咁「通情達理」先係好事？<br />\n<br />\n大公文匯轟馬道立「迴避改革」　引烈顯倫斥聲明「了無新意」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2217738\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2217738</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"14e5b4bf620bafbcb77815fb306de97c1f64e0c2","tid":2267953,"uid":6237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac4f54c848da5f575338ed5d743278146d67ee83","tid":2267953,"uid":365024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d056b82aca24fa2034f9d5a5d474d31db43daca","tid":2267953,"uid":6237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T12:40:16.000Z","msg":"人地就係知道你地只會守原則<br />\n先比人玩到聲到唔敢出<br />\n法律係人訂, 死守法律而唔變通就會好似今日香港咁<br />\n我